{"tid":528347,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"《垃圾支那黑錢球會》米蘭收購涉嫌洗黑錢？傳貝盧斯科尼和李勇鴻被調查","createTime":"2018-01-13T16:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T21:43:21.000Z","uid":124292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ccbe3956d9377ca15aac12d2a7402fbd9981777c","tid":528347,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T16:34:05.000Z","msg":"據意大利媒體報道，由於出售AC米蘭過程中涉嫌洗黑錢，貝盧斯科尼正在接受調查。<br />\n<br />\n2017年4月，當時身陷債務之中AC米蘭被出售給了李勇鴻，總額高達7.2億歐元，意大利媒體《新聞報》和Secolo XIX稱這比球會實際價值高出了3億。<br />\n<br />\n對貝盧斯科尼、他的菲寧維斯特集團以及中國商人李勇鴻的調查已經開啓。這對於重回意大利政壇的貝盧斯科尼來說可不是好消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://app.football-italia.net/?referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.football-italia.net%2F115522%2Fmilan-money-laundering-investigation#article/footballitalia-115522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapp.football-italia.net%2F%3Freferrer%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.football-italia.net%252F115522%252Fmilan-money-laundering-investigation%23article%2Ffootballitalia-115522&d=DAvTgABvU1htLMBbKnqBP%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=9f36f151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://app.football-italia.net/?referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.football-italia.net%2F115522%2Fmilan-money-laundering-investigation#article/footballitalia-115522</a>"},{"pid":"828446ceb0ae92d1b7784c79788636a972369964","tid":528347,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T19:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ff2879cf928be4922d6fa7c8f5964836f9376a","tid":528347,"uid":61228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T20:29:05.000Z","msg":"西波"},{"pid":"bfb4c6f01d84207704b8a7043754a9fe6f30ce4d","tid":528347,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T21:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}